import React from 'react' import {Container, Row, Col, Form} from 'react-bootstrap' import Title from './Title' import {useSelector} from 'react-redux' function Profile(history){ const {isLoggedIn, userData} = useSelector(state =>({ isLoggedIn: state.user.isLoggedIn, userData: state.user.payload })) if(isLoggedIn==false || userData==null){ alert('잘못된 페이지'); history.replace('/') } console.log(userData) const {username, email} = userData return(
<Container> <Row className="justify-content-md-center"> <Col xs lg={10}> <Form onSubmit={onClickHandler} > <Form.Group controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1"> <Form.Label>ID</Form.Label> <Form.Control name = 'username' value = {username} onChange={onChangeHandler} placeholder="ID를 입력해주세요" /> </Form.Group> <br/> <Form.Group controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1"> <Form.Label>EMAIL</Form.Label> <Form.Control name = 'email' value = {email} onChange={onChangeHandler} placeholder="email을 입력해주세요" /> </Form.Group> <br/> <Button type="submit">Register</Button> </Form> </Col> </Row> </Container> </div> ); } export default Profile
